{"tid":1287420,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"［反送中］大家可唔可以幫下老婆婆","createTime":"2019-07-05T07:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T23:36:47.000Z","uid":148778,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"760c90ae42466d3189b451fd9c4ff84053f05d59","tid":1287420,"uid":148778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:59:05.000Z","msg":"你見唔見到佢地好慘㗎，為咗一個幾毫企喺地鐵站幾個鐘收報紙<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n報紙示意圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZJnqr76.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZJnqr76.png&h=5f4cca2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實大家可以每人攞一份俾佢哋<br />\n<br />\n每日文匯都喺地鐵站附近有依d免費嘢去荼毒無知市民、分化香港<br />\n<br />\n亦成為我哋教育上一、兩代嘅阻力<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LECqr8q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLECqr8q.png&h=9c33b6f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我哋應該一人攞一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，避免俾d仲未識分辯是非嘅人睇，咁派嗰個又可以快手收工，d婆婆又可以快d走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而對於同cctvb作風相似嘅頭條日報，大家順手都都d婆婆攞埋啦<br />\n<br />\n香港真係好需要你嘅幫助㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3654a5841a66bfeb3ffa2a7d4be3c8996ebd5ffe","tid":1287420,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:01:25.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={S